------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The text material in this corpus consists of either abstracts or full
text of scientific publications. Abstracts are generally considered to
be exempt of copyright claims. All full text articles are from Open
Access publications released under a Creative Commons Attribution (CC
BY) license. Brat annotations are similarly released under a Creative
Commons Attribution (CC BY) license
(http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/).


